description: B & W Food Truck is making its way through LA and serving up a delicious Asian twist on burgers and other American comfort classics. Their menu features favorites like…Fried chicken wings tossed in a variety of tasty sauces (Lemon Pepper, BBQ Sesame Seed, Honey Sriracha, etc…) with a side of savory furikake coleslaw, “UFO Burgers”- juicy Angus beef patty with a crispy cheese ring, fresh tomato, onion, crisp lettuce, mayo, and B & W’s special sauce “Loco Moco”- Angus double patty with rice, rich gravy, topped with an egg & green onionWith all this and much more, if you’ve got big cravings for big flavors, be sure to come by B & W!
name: B & W Food Truck
